-- Russia c.bank says shifts rouble's trading band by 35 kopecks
-- 
-- Fri Oct 31, 2014 03:09AM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, Oct 31 (Reuters) - Russia's central bank said on Friday it had shifted the boundaries of its floating rouble corridor by 35 kopecks a day earlier, following market interventions to curb the pace of the currency's decline.

